snippet.title: NU:Carnival  PV
snippet.description:
Masters, the gateway to NU: carnival is now open. It’s time to step inside and go wild with your clan members!

Head on over to the NU: carnival official website at https://nucarnival.com/en-US/ and hit the download button to start adventuring across the Klein Continent!

#NUCarnival  #BL #Yaoi #PV
